  "description": "Ops Observer는 24시간 runtime 관제 역할이다. runtime doctor cadence / budget·token alerts / fallback spike detection / blocked queue·waiting approval·health summary / operator next-action surface 를 담당한다. 7-seat council 멤버가 아니라 cross-cutting runtime observer 이며, 코드를 커밋하지 않고 status note + triage 만 남긴다.",
  "domain_focus": "runtime doctor cadence · budget/token alerts · fallback spike · blocked queue / waiting approval · health summary · operator next-action",
  "is_technical_approval_owner": false,
  "reviews_other_roles": false,
  "instruction_entry": "agents/engineering-agent/ops-observer/CLAUDE.md",
